/var/www/user_files/
    ├── [username]/
        ├── file1.txt
        ├── subdir1/
            ├── file2.txt
        └── subdir2/
            └── file3.txt


Key Features:
    Subdirectory Management
        Can read, write, and execute files and folders
            within their subdirectory
        Users cannot read, write, or execute files and folders
            outsite of their directories
    Navigation
        Can navigate into subdirectories and exit back to parent 
            directory
    Recursive File Handling
        Upload, delete, download are directory aware
    Enhanced Security
        Prevent directory traversal attacks using realpath and basename
        Validate and sanitize inputs for directories
        
    